cause.description:
a group to show respect to the president of the United States.
1. The President deserves respect.
2. The President makes tough decisions, and deserves support.
3. The president is a human being, too.
cause.mission: Show support for the president of the united states, regardless of who it is, what party its from, decisions it makes. This person is the president and deserves respect.
cause.name: Support the President
